    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "ch4pW",
      "x": 1590,
      "y": 0,
      "name": "M-Home-Dark-375-Notes",
      "width": 600,
      "height": 1680,
      "fill": "#1F1D19",
      "layout": "vertical",
      "gap": 20,
      "padding": 32,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "xPeRH",
          "fill": "#FAF8F3",
          "content": "M-Home-Dark-375 · 说明 Frame",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 22,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "qNCOA",
          "fill": "#C9C2B0",
          "content": "基于 Schema-v1 · Dark 模式 · 视口 375 × 812 · 同一回访场景（与 Light 版并列对照）· data-theme=dark · 由 prefers-color-scheme: dark 触发或用户手动切换",
          "lineHeight": 1.6,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "6ugu6",
          "fill": "#FAF8F3",
          "content": "1. 两模式差异说明（Schema §2.5.4）",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 18,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "exW98",
          "fill": "#E5E0D3",
          "content": "• 所有 Surface Token 切换到 Dark：bg-primary #FAF8F3→#1A1814 / bg-secondary #F2EFE7→#1F1D19 / bg-tertiary #EDF4F2→#152523 / bg-elevated #FFFFFF→#26231E / border-subtle #E5E0D3→#33302A\n• 所有 Foreground Token 反转：fg-primary #1A1814→#FAF8F3 / fg-secondary #4A4438→#E5E0D3 / fg-muted #6B6456→#C9C2B0\n• 朝代卡四态 bg 全部切换：perfect #F5D3CC→#5C221B / cleared #F1E0C4→#50351B / active #D6E6E1→#223936 / locked #F2EFE7→#1F1D19\n• Accent 系列明度上提 18%：celadon 500→400（#4A7C74→#6FA89F）/ cinnabar 500→400（#C04A3A→#CD5B46）/ ochre 500→400（#B67B3D→#C4934D）\n• 阴影 → 发光：shadow-sm/md/lg 的 alpha 0.06-0.14 → 0.4-0.6（替换为半透明黑发光，实际 Pencil 稿中省略）\n• 切换动画：body/* transition 仅 color/background-color/border-color/fill/stroke，≤ 200ms ease-in-out（禁 width/height/padding/margin/transform）",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "M3T0l",
          "fill": "#FAF8F3",
          "content": "2. Dark 对比度 [待验证 webaim]",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 18,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "ItOYH",
          "fill": "#E5E0D3",
          "content": "• 米白 #FAF8F3 on 墨黑 #1A1814（fg-primary on bg-primary）→ ~15:1 ✅\n• 淡褐灰 #E5E0D3 on 墨黑 #1A1814（fg-secondary）→ ~12:1 ✅\n• 灰褐 #C9C2B0 on 墨黑 #1A1814（fg-muted）→ ~9:1 ✅\n• 朱砂明 #EBA89B on 墨深 #5C221B（perfect fg on bg）→ [待验证，预计 ~6:1]\n• 杏黄 #E4C697 on 墨褐 #50351B（cleared fg on bg）→ [待验证，预计 ~6:1]\n• 青瓷淡 #B5D0C7 on 墨青 #223936（active fg on bg）→ [待验证，预计 ~6:1]\n• 中墨褐 #6B6456 on 墨夜 #1F1D19（locked fg on bg）→ ~3:1 ⚠️ 低于 AA 但属 disabled 豁免\n\n⚠️ 已知风险（Design Token §1.4）：Dark 模式 accent 底上的白字 #FAF8F3 on #6FA89F ~3.2:1 不达 AA 4.5；Token 定义了 fg-on-accent=#1A1814 兜底。本稿中 Logo 底字已修正为 #1A1814；朝代卡 icon 底上的 ✓/★/▶ 字符当前仍为白——SCHEMA-DELTA #003 登记为 P1 待 r-qa 实测对比度后裁决（若失败则 batch replace 到 #1A1814）",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "hFd66",
          "fill": "#FAF8F3",
          "content": "3. 图像资产策略（Schema §2.5.5 · SC-TH8）",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 18,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "S2BpP",
          "fill": "#E5E0D3",
          "content": "• 10 朝代插画（答题页主视觉 / 卡册卡封面）：❌ 不换，单版本 + dark 加 shadow-perfect-glow 0.4 alpha 外发光增强识别（本稿暂用 emoji 占位，资产待补）\n• 10 枚徽章：⚠️ SVG 使用 currentColor 自适应 · 朱砂通过 Token 双套自动切换\n• Logo「祖」字：⚠️ 当前为 SVG 单色模板，两模式共用；真实 Logo 出来后若为彩色则需双版本\n• 空态插画：线条 SVG + currentColor 单版本",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "2mfUZ",
          "fill": "#FAF8F3",
          "content": "4. 切换按钮行为（Schema §2.5.1 · FW14）",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 18,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "rsGTX",
          "fill": "#E5E0D3",
          "content": "• ☀/☾/⚙ 三态按钮 · 顶栏 ☀ icon（Light）在本视图变 ☾（Dark）· aria-label=nav.theme_switch_label\n• tap = 循环 system → light → dark → system · 长按（≥500ms）弹 Bottom Sheet 三选 listbox\n• localStorage.theme 写入；inline script 在 <head> 最前读取（FW13 FOUC 防护）\n• 本项目 SPA 无 SSR hydration 错配顾虑",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13
        }
      ]
    },
