          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "M-Quiz-Light-375 · 说明 Frame",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 22,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "k8Nip",
          "fill": "#6B6456",
          "content": "基于 Schema-v1 · Light 模式 · 视口 375 × 812 · 场景：答题中，第 3/5 题，已选 B「大禹」未提交（selected 态）· 朝代=夏 · 布局模式=Layout Shifter（与 1024 桌面两栏重设）",
          "lineHeight": 1.6,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "aIZy4",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "1. 交互说明",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 17,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "N7nCt",
          "fill": "#4A4438",
          "content": "① ← 返回（40×40，触控区 r-frontend 扩展 48×48）→ 打开 ExitConfirm Bottom Sheet，默认焦点 quiz.confirm_exit.continue「继续答题」（MI6 保守默认）\n② 夏（H1 dynasty name）= 非交互\n③ ●●●○○ 进度点（radiogroup role=progressbar aria-valuenow=3）：当前第 3 题青瓷填充 + 朱砂 ring，已答的 1/2 全青瓷，未答 4/5 border-subtle\n④ 朝代插画 160h 青瓷浅底（🏛占位，真实资产见 ASSET-LIST #002）· 底部渐变遮罩 linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(250,248,243,0.85)) 使「第 3/5 题」label 可读\n⑤ 「第 3/5 题」label = fg-muted · type-caption 13/1.4\n⑥ 题干「夏朝的开国君主是谁？」= fs-h3 22/1.4 · Source Han Serif SC 600 · :lang(zh) 行高应实为 1.7（见 Schema §4.2）\n⑦ 选项 A/B/C/D：role=radiogroup，键盘 ↑↓ 切换；每选项 min-height 56 (PROJ-TT1 > 52) · 间距 12\n   A/C/D = 默认态（白底 · 浅灰边 1px · A/B/C/D 前缀圆徽章 32×32 浅底黑字）\n   B = 已选未提交态（青瓷浅底 #EDF4F2 · 青瓷边 2px · 前缀徽章青瓷填充白字 · 右侧「已选」label 青瓷色 12px）\n⑧ Sticky CTA bar 72-88px（含 safe-area padding-bottom 24）· 顶部 border-subtle · 青瓷主按钮 56h「下一题」（此时 B 已选，按钮启用；若未选则 CTA disabled 灰态）· aria-label=quiz.cta.next",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "h4X0R",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "2. 状态流转",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 17,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "1GSan",
          "fill": "#4A4438",
          "content": "tap B → B 进入 selected 态（本稿即为此态）\ntap Next CTA → submit → 反馈态（B 切换为 correct 态 = answer-correct-bg #E7F2EC + jade-500 边 + ✓ icon；正确答案 label 下方 aria-live=polite 播报 quiz.feedback_correct）\n若 B 错（假设正确答案是 C 启）→ B = answer-wrong-bg #F8E4E4 + carmine-500 边 + ? icon · C 额外显示 answer-correct 态 + 「正确答案是」label\n反馈态下方 expand 解释文 ≤ 35em CJK / 65ch Latin\n再 tap Next → 切到第 4 题 + motion-flip-exit+enter (240 + 360ms)\n第 5 题 Next CTA 文案切换 quiz.cta.settle「看结果」→ 跳 /result/:dynastyId",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "s4psq",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "3. 响应式 / i18n / 无障碍要点",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 17,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "a0xCl",
          "fill": "#4A4438",
          "content": "• 768：朝代插画 160→240h；选项单列居中加宽 max-width 600；Sticky CTA → 内嵌非 sticky\n• 1024：Layout Shifter 两栏（左 40% 全高插画 · 右 60% 题干+选项+内嵌 CTA，max-width 640）\n• 答题页顶栏禁语言切换（Schema §3 模块 B · interaction-brief §7.1：防 locale 切换导致题目错位）\n• 手势禁 swipe（MI5 · 防儿童误滑走题）\n• ESC = 打开 ExitConfirm（A8）\n• 焦点顺序：返回 → A → B → C → D → Next（Tab）+ ↑↓ 在 radiogroup 内切换\n• 对比度 Light [待验证]：#1A1814 on #FAF8F3 ~15:1 ✅；#2F4E4A on #EDF4F2（B 已选字）~7:1 ✅；#FAF8F3 on #4A7C74（CTA 白字）~4.8:1 临界需实测\n• CJK 行高：题干 :lang(zh) line-height 1.7（Schema §4.2 实现提示）\n• 文案膨胀：「下一题」3 字 → en「Next」4 字符；「已选」2 字 → en「Selected」8 字符（200% 膨胀）· CTA padding 弹性满足",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "8xV73",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "4. Token 映射（本 Frame IMPLEMENTATION-GUIDE 抽取）",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 17,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "Nofd4",
          "fill": "#4A4438",
          "content": "页底 $bg-primary #FAF8F3 · 顶栏同色 · 分隔 $border-subtle #E5E0D3 1px\n进度点 active=$accent-primary #4A7C74 + ring=$accent-secondary #C04A3A 2px · 未答=$border-subtle #E5E0D3\n插画区 $bg-tertiary #EDF4F2 · 图标色 $accent-primary · 实际资产待 visual-designer 出图\n题干 $fg-primary #1A1814 · font-display (Source Han Serif SC)\n选项默认 $bg-elevated #FFFFFF + $border-strong #C9C2B0 1px + $radius-md 10\n选项 selected $answer-hover-bg #EDF4F2 + $answer-selected-border #4A7C74 2px · 前缀 accent-primary bg + fg-on-accent 字\nCTA 主 $accent-primary #4A7C74 + $fg-on-accent #FAF8F3 + $radius 12",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
