    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "U1U6B",
      "x": 848,
      "y": 4000,
      "name": "T-Home-768-Notes (Light+Dark 通用差异)",
      "width": 600,
      "height": 1200,
      "fill": "#F2EFE7",
      "layout": "vertical",
      "gap": 16,
      "padding": 32,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "DzsN9",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "T-Home-768 · 说明 Frame（Light + Dark 通用）",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 22,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "LV089",
          "fill": "#6B6456",
          "content": "基于 Schema-v1 · 视口 768 × 1200 · 平板竖屏 + 小尺寸 iPad / 浏览器中等宽度 · Dark 版色值全部走 Semantic Token 双套自动切换（见 design-tokens §7）",
          "lineHeight": 1.6,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "Y9pt0",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "1. 相对 M-375 的变化（响应式差异）",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 17,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "78bv8",
          "fill": "#4A4438",
          "content": "• 顶栏 56 → 64 · Logo 从 icon-only 改为 icon + 简写品牌名「老祖宗」· 工具按钮从纯 icon 改为 icon + 文字标签（语言 / 主题 / 卡册）· padding-x 16 → 24\n• 欢迎区 88 → 104 · H 标题 fs-h1 →  fs-display（24→30）· body 完整显示（mobile 仅标题 + progress_summary）\n• 朝代图谱：纵向 10 卡 → **2×5 网格**（5 行 × 2 列）· 每卡 72h → 140h · 卡内布局从 horizontal（icon+name+badge 一行）改为 horizontal + text 内部两行（name + era），badge 吸附在底部（期望：r-frontend 用 `align-items: stretch` 让 block 填满）\n• 朝代卡的 era 副标题**显示**（mobile 本应隐藏，但纵向单列保留 — 见 SCHEMA-DELTA #001）\n• 错题入口 72h → 88h · 「再来看一眼 (3 题)」文案一致\n• 卡册缩略：横向滑动 5 缩略 → 单行 5 缩略（不溢出，2×5 网格的主宽占优）\n• 本断点**独有组件**：无（Mobile-375 有 sticky CTA bar · Desktop-1024 有右侧次级栏）",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "DSvLF",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "2. 文案 / 多语言",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 17,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "sgu9E",
          "fill": "#4A4438",
          "content": "• 所有文案从 locale-zh.json 取（en 膨胀 40-70%，见 Schema §5.1）\n• 朝代名「三国」→ en「Three Kingdoms」14 字符 · 卡内 name H26 可能导致两行，min-height 140 保证容纳\n• 工具标签「主题」2 字 → en「Theme」5 字符（150% 膨胀），padding 弹性满足\n• 欢迎 progress_summary「上次你走到了秦朝。已闯过 3/10 关 · 全对 1/10」→ en 变长可能两行，wel 高度 104 考虑 → en 下改 auto-height（min-height 104）",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "NVSFT",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "3. 无障碍 / Token",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 17,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "rtcPV",
          "fill": "#4A4438",
          "content": "• 焦点顺序：Logo → 语言 → 主题 → 卡册 → 欢迎区（非聚焦）→ 朝代卡 1 → 2 → ... → 10（grid 内方向键 ↑↓ 跨行 / ←→ 跨列）→ 错题入口 → 卡册缩略\n• 触摸目标：工具按钮 44h + padding ≥ 12 · 触控区 ≥ 48（PROJ-TT1）\n• 卡片 hover（desktop/pointer:fine 触发）：translateY(-2px) + elevation-2 + hover tooltip 显示朝代简介 40-60 字（mobile 触屏不触发）\n• Token 使用同 M-375（见那份 Notes 第 8 节 Token 映射），只是尺寸阶梯放大：fs-display(30) · fs-h2(22/24) · card-radius 16 → 20",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "j70E4",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "4. Light / Dark 差异速查",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 17,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "RbvYT",
          "fill": "#4A4438",
          "content": "Dark 版（x=1608 右侧）所有 Token 自动切换，对比度 [待验证]：\n• fg-primary 白 on bg-primary 墨黑：~15:1 ✅\n• Perfect 卡 fg #EBA89B on bg #5C221B：~6:1 ✅\n• Cleared 卡 fg #E4C697 on bg #50351B：~6:1 ✅\n• Active 卡 fg #B5D0C7 on bg #223936：~7:1 ✅\n• Locked 卡 fg #6B6456 on bg #1F1D19：~3:1 ⚠️ disabled 豁免 + 🔒 icon 形状区分\n• 错题入口 fg #EBA89B on bg #3A1616：~6:1 ✅",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "FKloC",
      "x": 848,
      "y": 5350,
      "name": "T-Quiz-768-Notes",
      "width": 600,
      "height": 1200,
      "fill": "#F2EFE7",
      "layout": "vertical",
      "gap": 16,
      "padding": 32,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "XEmvy",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "T-Quiz-768 · 说明 Frame（Light + Dark 通用）",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 22,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "RwPtV",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "1. 相对 M-375 的变化",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 17,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "ErUbx",
          "fill": "#4A4438",
          "content": "• 顶栏 56 → 64 · 增加「第 3/5 题」文字补充（mobile 只用进度点）\n• 朝代插画 160 → **240** 高（Schema §3 模块 B）· 占位 🏛 字号放大 72→120\n• 题干区 padding 20/16 → **40/24** · max-width 600 居中（R3 行宽 CJK ≤ 35em 满足）· fs-h3 22 → 30\n• 4 选项按钮 56h → 64h · max-width 600（同 body inner）· 保留单列\n• **Sticky CTA bar 移除** → 改为内嵌右对齐 CTA（inline padding-x 40）· 这是 Mobile-First 核心差异（MobileFirst 硬约束 MF1：移动端独有 sticky CTA）\n• 本断点独有：无（CTA 内嵌而非 sticky）",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "5Jsfs",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "2. 交互与文案同 M-375",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 17,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "rDNKK",
          "fill": "#4A4438",
          "content": "• 文案 100% 从 locale-zh.json 的 quiz.* 取：quiz.progress / quiz.feedback_* / quiz.cta.next / quiz.confirm_exit.*\n• B 已选未提交态：answer-hover-bg + answer-selected-border 2px + 前缀 accent 徽章 · 未选时 CTA disabled 态（本稿显示启用）\n• 答题页禁语言切换（interaction-brief §7.1 · Schema §3 模块 B）\n• 手势禁 swipe · 键盘 ↑↓ 在 radiogroup 内切换\n• 对比度同 M-375（Design Token §1.4）· Dark CTA 白字风险同样适用",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "xt0aL",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "3. Dark 版（x=1608）差异",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 17,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "c7ULt",
          "fill": "#4A4438",
          "content": "同 M-375 dark：所有 Token 切换，插画区底 #EDF4F2 → #152523 + 遮罩色 rgba(26,24,20,0.88)；选项 B 已选字 #B5D0C7 on #152523 ~7:1；CTA 白字 on #6FA89F 风险在 SCHEMA-DELTA #003 登记",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "8LWfr",
      "x": 1104,
      "y": 9000,
      "name": "D-Home-1024-Notes",
      "width": 600,
      "height": 900,
