        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "Tm2JF",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "D-Quiz-1024 · 说明 Frame（Light + Dark 通用 · Layout Shifter 核心断点）",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 22,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "IF2wV",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "1. 核心变化：Layout Shifter 单栏 → 两栏重设",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 17,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "RdJCf",
          "fill": "#4A4438",
          "content": "• 从 T-768 的「顶栏 + 插画 240h + 题干 + 选项 + 内嵌 CTA」单栏堆叠，**重设**为左栏 40%（410px 全高朝代插画）+ 右栏 60%（~614px · 题干 + 4 选项 + CTA）\n• 左栏插画成为主视觉：占全高 655px 青瓷浅底 + 大 emoji 200px 占位 · 真实资产需要有意识设计为纵向构图\n• 右栏 padding 48 · 题干 fs-h1 32（比 T-768 的 30 再放大）· 选项 64h → 68h · CTA 56h 内嵌右对齐\n• Layout Shifter 意味着 DOM 结构差异：r-frontend MUST 用 display: grid（1024+）/ display: flex column（< 1024）而非 CSS-only 改宽度",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "9OdW6",
          "fill": "#1A1814",
          "content": "2. 交互同 M-375 / T-768",
          "lineHeight": 1.3,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 17,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "fpucU",
          "fill": "#4A4438",
          "content": "• 禁 swipe / 禁语言切换 / ESC = ExitConfirm · 键盘 Tab: 返回 → A → B → C → D → Next\n• Desktop hover 态（pointer:fine）：选项浮起 translateY(-2px) + answer-hover-bg\n• 焦点 ring 3px 青瓷环（$shadow-focus-ring）所有断点共用\n• 对比度、资产策略、Dark 差异同 T-768 Quiz Notes",
          "lineHeight": 1.7,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 13,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    },
